data.name: ReadFips
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, COUNTY_DESC from CKT_FIPS where (LOCATION = @location) and (COUNTY = @county) and ([STATE] = @state)

data.name: ReadTribunal
data.value: select top(1) JUDICIAL_DIVISION, TRIBUNAL_NM, FIP_LOCATION, JUDICIAL_DISTRICT, IDENTIFIER, FIP_COUNTY, FIP_STATE from CKT_TRIBUNAL where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: ReadTribunalFeeInformation
data.value: select TRB_ID, TRIBUNAL_FEE_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, RATE, CAP, DISCONTINUE_DATE, DESCRIPTION from CKT_TRIB_FEE_INFO where @trbId = TRB_ID order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc
